### HYMN L

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2005001">1</span></span>What newest
of imploring hymns shall, then, the zealous mortal  
   sing?  
  For have not they who laud his might and Indra-power won for  
   themselves the light of heaven?  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_2005002">2</span></span>When shall
they keep the Law and praise thee mid the Gods?  
  Who counts as Rishi and as sage?  
  When wilt thou ever, Indra, Bounteous Lord, come nigh to  
   presser's or to praiser's call?

